WE WILL ANALYZE THE X-RAY DATA TO DETERMINE THE PHYSICAL PROPERTIES OF THE EMITTING PLASMAS, (SUCH AS LX, AND T) AND APPLY PULSATING-INDUCED SHOCK MODELS.
